    imageD: {fileID: 0}
  - layout: {fileID: 470820575514630869, guid: 1a4ce467c9bbd91459e6f1d16a4f9a9e, type: 3}
    textA: Skinwalker Stag
    textB: Some wear the skin poorly. The legs bend wrong. The head lags behind the
      body.
    textC: Do not look away. It cannot hold the shape forever. It relies on darkness
      to hide, so attack it with light.
    textD: 
    imageA: {fileID: 8191607871805606840, guid: 7909af0775c51c643afc2a28723c90f6, type: 3}
    imageB: {fileID: -8579180617657454444, guid: ae45ff052776b1840be37ac3d2a07621, type: 3}
    imageC: {fileID: 0}
    imageD: {fileID: 0}
  - layout: {fileID: 4469434606004700145, guid: b1f56c105ade1124b882fddd07899040, type: 3}
    textA: Many-Eyed Stag
    textB: Break the sight!
    textC: And the body follows.
    textD: 'There are others that do not hide. They watch....Not just from the body.


      The
      eyes grow where they are needed. On walls. In the dark. Behind you....


      If
      it cannot see you, it cannot hunt you!

'
    imageA: {fileID: -5926201026390796380, guid: 7bda3dac18202074c9e330f707aabd49, type: 3}
    imageB: {fileID: 0}
    imageC: {fileID: 0}
